Name: Square Head Zombies 2 - FPS Game
About the game: After killing all zombies in the first game, the zombie plague spread through the world, now you will face more enemies in Square Head Zombies 2 . You will face zombies that attack at a short distance and from long distances, some are slow, others are extremely fast. More zombies, more challenges. Fight with zombies in the shopping, big cities, beaches, offices, farms. There is a lot of places that you will find enemies. Game Features: - Different type of zombies - Ammo is not infinite anymore like in the first game, collect ammo through the levels to be able to kill all zombies - New levels - New achievements
